reviewText: I thought it contained Dr. No, Goldfinger, and From Russia with Love as another reviewer wrote. When the videos arrived, the set instead contained You Only Live Twice, Diamonds are Forever, and Thunderball. Beware
There are three excellant movies in the set - they are Dr. NO, GOLDFINGER, and FROM RUSSIA WITH LOVE.
Very fast and claver. As a die hard 007 fan that I am,this is THE best James Bond movie Sean Connery ever had the chance to play in,no strings attached.
